{"type": "article", "id": 9045, "title": "Nike SB Free 系列鞋款", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-30T07:16:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235053jeVpoGzTLkZOUfr2.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tJames Jarvis 是一位来自英国的艺术家，也是目前全世界最抢手的插画师之一，他最近和 Nike 联合推出了 Nike SB Free 系列鞋款，鞋面上是 James Jarvis 招牌式的手绘涂鸦，鞋身有灰绿与鲜红色 Swoosh 标识，透露着浓浓的街头风。这款鞋子将会在 5 月 9 日开始在门店和<a href=\"www.nike.com\" target=\"_blank\"> Nike 官方网站</a>发售。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235049oeaOS5uyjVAhBZdN.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235050yja3g9iG4XhTKRsA.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235050mS798qW3KEa0RwQv.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.55833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235051JrKzdNfwZvinuUD5.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.54259259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235051xALImWHj5YlqT3yk.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.56111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235052kdwCxv4HEfG9eQnP.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235052URbQGsIYXM7liALv.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}